data.title: Does adding techron to gasoline help a car engine run better?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 7): Car engines benefit from Techron because it cleans the fuel system, increases fuel efficiency, and decreases emissions. Techron is a fuel injector cleaner that may also be used to clean intake valves and combustion chambers, among other parts of the fuel system.
